 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Folkeroy was born in 1193, in Devon, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Mrs. John Folkeroy. He died in his hometown."},"et":{"1193–":"1193–Surnud","1196–Female":"1196–Surnud","1220–Male":"1220–Surnud","1193–Male":"1193–Surnud","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1193–":"1193–Kuollut","1196–Female":"1196–Kuollut","1220–Male":"1220–Kuollut","1193–Male":"1193–Kuollut","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1193–":"1193–Décédé","1196–Female":"1196–Décédée","1220–Male":"1220–Décédé","1193–Male":"1193–Décédé","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"John Folkeroy est né en 1193, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Mrs. John Folkeroy. Il est décédé dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1193–":"1193–Verstorben","1196–Female":"1196–Verstorben","1220–Male":"1220–Verstorben","1193–Male":"1193–Verstorben","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"John Folkeroy wurde 1193 in Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Mrs. John Folkeroy mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1193–":"1193–Desede","1196–Female":"1196–Desede","1220–Male":"1220–Desede","1193–Male":"1193–Desede","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1193–":"1193–elhunyt","1196–Female":"1196–elhunyt","1220–Male":"1220–elhunyt","1193–Male":"1193–elhunyt","1220":"1220","1196":"1196","1193":"1193","Devon, England, United King